        <updateDate>2019-04-19T22:11:08Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Helping Startups Continue to Grow Act </b></p> <p>This bill allows certain issuers of securities regulated as emerging growth companies to continue operating under such regulations, including those related to reduced disclosures and other exemptions, for an additional five years.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
